# Ad-hoc developer artefacts that shouldn't ship:
# - Diagnostic ZIPs and unpacked folders the user generates while
#   troubleshooting are large, contain timestamps and PII-ish hostnames,
#   and have no value in source control.
# - Editor / agent state directories.
# - Throwaway scripts under _diag_temp and ad-hoc probe scripts.
diag-extract/
diag-extract-new/
_diag*/
*-diagnostics-*.zip
.tmp/
zips/
.kiro/
.vscode/
vpn-tunnel-enforcer/scripts/probe-subscription.mjs
vpn-tunnel-enforcer/scripts/inspect-bundle.mjs


